Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.54,0:00:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like a cruel angel{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.55,0:00:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Become a legend, young boy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.39,0:00:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When a blue wind{\i0}\N{\i1}Knocks on the door to your heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.15,0:00:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You just gaze back at me{\i0}\N{\i1}And smile oh so gently{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So eager for something{\i0}\N{\i1}You touch so softly{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.12,0:00:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those innocent eyes{\i0}\N{\i1}Know nothing of the fate that awaits{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.67,0:00:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But one day, you will realize{\i0}\N{\i1}That upon your back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.18,0:01:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have wings{\i0}\N{\i1}You can fly to the faraway future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.77,0:01:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The cruel angel's thesis{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day, you'll take off through a window{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.15,0:01:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If your overflowing pathos{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.91,0:01:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leads you to betray your memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.62,0:01:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then embrace the heavens and shine bright{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.29,0:01:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Become legend, young boy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.34,0:01:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good morning, Shinji. How are you feeling?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm used to it. It's not so bad now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Glad to hear it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eva egress points, emergency{\i0}\N{\i1}ordnance structures, recovery points...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.48,0:01:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-Do you have them all memorized?{\i0}\N-I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's go over it one more time, then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.03,0:01:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An Eva usually runs off an external,{\i0}\N{\i1}cabled power feed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When it switches to internal battery{\i0}\N{\i1}in an emergency,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}capacity limitations mean{\i0}\N{\i1}it can only run at full for one minute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can run for five minutes at most{\i0}\N{\i1}by using a low gain mode.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.87,0:02:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's as far as our science can go.{\i0}\N{\i1}Understood?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.17,0:02:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then we'll pick up from yesterday.{\i0}\N{\i1}Starting induction mode.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Center the target... and pull the trigger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Keep calm. Center the target.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.19,0:02:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull the trigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.19,0:02:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed that Shinji was willing\Nto go through with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He does whatever he's told.\NThat's how he makes his life easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:03:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Center the target, pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now we go to Matsuzaki,{\i0}\N{\i1}where Natsuko Shinohara is waiting!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hello! Good morning! Shinohara here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This morning, we're here to do{\i0}\N{\i1}some diving at Matsuzaki in West Izu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Misato? It's morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got off duty...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need to show up\Nbefore sunset today, so let me sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, today's Thursday!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Take out the burnable garbage, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you gotten settled in at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay... Have a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are things working out\Nwith the new boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Boyfriend? Oh, you mean Shinji.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been two weeks since{\i0}\N{\i1}he started school, and nothing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nobody ever calls him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Calls him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a necessity, so I got him{\i0}\N{\i1}a cell phone a while ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But there's no sign of him ever using it{\i0}\N{\i1}or anyone ever calling him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm starting to think{\i0}\N{\i1}he doesn't have any friends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji might be the sort of person\Nwho can't make friends easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever heard of\Nthe Hedgehog's Dilemma?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hedgehog? Those spiky animals?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hedgehogs have a hard time sharing{\i0}\N{\i1}warmth with other hedgehogs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The closer they get, the more{\i0}\N{\i1}they hurt each other with their quills.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}People are also like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think some part of Shinji{\i0}\N{\i1}is afraid to take that risk{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}because he's afraid of being hurt.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He'll figure it out eventually.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Part of growing up is trying again{\i0}\N{\i1}and again and using trial and error{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to work out the right distance{\i0}\N{\i1}to avoid hurting each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Class Rep?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you deliver all those\Nstudy guides like I asked?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it doesn't seem like\Nanyone's home at Tohji's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Suzuhara are friends,\Naren't you, Aida?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you worried that he's\Nmissed school for two weeks?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:05:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he got hurt badly or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In that incident with the giant robot?\NBut the TV said no one got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. You saw the crater\Nat Mt. Takanosu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Units were called up from\Nnot only Iruma and Komatsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but even from Misawa and Kyushu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There must have been way more than ten\Nor 20 casualties. Some fatalities, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-Tohji!\N-Suzuhara!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, damn.\NThere sure are a lot fewer of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They evacuated. They all transferred out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what happens when there's\Na huge battle in the middle of your city.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you're the only guy that loves this.\NGetting to see a firefight up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's up, Tohji? Why did you\Nstay home from school for so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get mixed up in that mess?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My kid sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My kid sister got buried\Nunder a pile of rubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She survived, but she's been\Nin the hospital ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My old man and uncle\Nwork at the labs, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't tear themselves away\Nfrom work right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.67,0:07:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I don't stay with her,\Nshe'd be all alone in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, the pilot of that damn robot\Nis totally worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He pisses me off so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's supposed to be on our side,\Nand he trashed the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,About that. Have you heard the rumors\Nabout the new transfer student?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Transfer student?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That kid over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He transferred in while you were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He showed up right after the battle.\NDon't you think that's fishy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, this is how humanity\Nwas faced with its greatest ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In the closing year of the 20th Century,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,a meteor of extraordinarily high mass\Nmade impact on Antarctica.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That continent of ice\Nwas melted in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sea levels rose,\Nthe planet's axis shifted,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:08:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and abnormal weather assaulted the globe,\Nthreatening all life on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Half of mankind,\Nalong with thousands of species,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,were forever lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what we now refer to\Nas the Second Impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.74,0:08:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Economic collapse,\Nethnic conflicts, and civil wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who survived\Nexperienced hell on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,ARE YOU REALLY THE PILOT OF THAT ROBOT?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In fifteen short years, we have\Nbounced back and rebuilt so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,While this is surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,IT'S TRUE, ISN'T IT?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...a testament to\Nthe greatness of mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it is also the result of the blood,\Nsweat, tears, and hard work
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of your fathers and mothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was living in Nebukawa at the time.\NBut that's now underwater...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Class isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go,\Nbossing everyone around again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-Give it a rest!\N-I will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.41,0:09:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wow!\N-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-So, how were you chosen?!\N-Was there a test or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-Weren't you scared?\N-What's the cockpit like?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well... All that stuff is secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-Aw, don't hold out on us!\N-What's the name of that robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know for sure, but everyone\Ncalls mine "Eva" or "Unit 01."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Any special attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They said it has something called a...\Na "something" Knife...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It uses vibration to...\NNo, ultrasound or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so cool!\NYou're the pride of our school!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And that brings us to--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's all for today.\N-Where do you live, Ikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All rise! Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, at least try to be polite\Nat the end of class, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, newbie. But I have to punch you.\NI couldn't live with myself otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, buddy.\NHis little sister got hurt in that battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just how he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I pilot that thing\Nbecause I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency call-up. I'll meet you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A special state of emergency has{\i0}\N{\i1}been declared for the Toukai region{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the surrounding mid-Kanto area.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All residents, proceed to your{\i0}\N{\i1}designated shelter immediately.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I repeat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Visual confirmation of target.{\i0}\N{\i1}Has entered territorial waters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All personnel to\Ncondition one battle stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger! Prepare for{\i0}\N{\i1}surface-to-air intercept!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Initiating deployment of Tokyo-3{\i0}\N{\i1}into combat configuration.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Retracting central block structures.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Retraction of central block structures,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as well as Wards 1 through 7,{\i0}\N{\i1}now complete.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Government and appropriate agencies{\i0}\N{\i1}have been notified.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Air defense systems currently{\i0}\N{\i1}operating at 48% capacity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Status of noncombatants and civilians?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Evacuation has been reported as completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,TOKYO-3 DISASTER PREVENTION DIV.\NAREA: 2000m2, MAX OCCUPANCY: 250
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Students in grades 1-9,{\i0}\N{\i1}stay with your class.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Residents, remain with other{\i0}\N{\i1}residents of your block.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing but text again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a press blackout.\NThey're keeping us civilians in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it,\Nthis is a once-in-a-lifetime deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The 4th Angel strikes\Nwhile Commander Ikari is away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sooner than we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Last time was after a 15-year gap.\NThis time, only three weeks went by.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Not very considerate of others, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Women hate people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What a waste of taxpayer money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Council is requesting\Nthat we launch an Evangelion again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Bunch of pushy jerks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We were going to do that anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Entry sequence has started.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1}Ionizing LCL.{\i0}\N{\i1}-Pressure clamps unlocked.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Father isn't here to watch,{\i0}\N{\i1}so why am I doing this again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was even beaten up because of it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I need to talk to you\Nabout something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In private.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey, Class Rep.\N-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.62,0:13:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to take a leak!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! You should have\Ndone that before we came here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to see one before I die, just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That fight up top?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way to know when or if\Nthe enemy will come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kensuke, you're a real piece of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! This might be\Nour only opportunity, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, please, help me unlock the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-Going outside might get you killed!\N-The same thing might happen in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If I might die either way,\NI want to see what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You dumbass. Nerv's there to stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly, and what is Nerv's\Ndecisive battle weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the new kid's robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He protected us in the last battle.\NAnd then you had to deck him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.24,0:14:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll all be dead\Nif he doesn't get in and pilot it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohji, isn't it your duty\Nto watch him fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a real slave to\Nyour passions, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinji, are you ready for launch?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:15:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Remember. Pallet rifle volley fire as{\i0}\N{\i1}you neutralize the enemy's A.T. Field.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like we practiced. Can you handle it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it was worth all the trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-A.T. Field raised.{\i0}\N-Center the target...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1}Proceed according to plan. Okay, Shinji?{\i0}\N-Pull the trigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.99,0:15:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That idiot! That smoke and dust\Nis obscuring the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?\NHe's getting his ass kicked already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're putting out a spare rifle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.51,0:16:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Grab it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinji? Shinji!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That beatdown\Nmust have really rattled him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Umbilical cable severed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva has switched to internal power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Active time remaining,\Nfour minutes, 53 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's headed right for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinji, are you okay? Shinji?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1}Damage report!{\i0}\N-{\i1}None. He's good to go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-Shinji's classmates?!\N-What are they doing there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why isn't he fighting back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because we're here?\NHis hands are tied!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unit 01 active time remaining,{\i0}\N{\i1}three minutes, 28 seconds!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinji, let those two into your cockpit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:18:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,After you've retrieved them, retreat!\NWe'll start over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can allow unauthorized\Ncivilians into that entry plug?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.37,0:18:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm authorizing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're overstepping your authority,\NCapt. Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01 active time remaining,\Nthree minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mission on hold under standing orders.\NEject the entry plug in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.22,0:18:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You two, get in! Hurry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this, water?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My camera! My camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Abnormalities in nerve circuits!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two foreign bodies\Nin the entry plug.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's noise mixed in\Nwith the nerve pulses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1}Use recovery route 34. Pull back to...{\i0}\N-Hey, newbie! She said to retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:18:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't run away. Don't run away.\N-Newbie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Progressive Knife equipped!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinji, obey my order! I said to retreat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinji!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.84,0:19:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01 active time remaining, 30 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty-eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Twenty-seven! Twenty-six!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Twenty-five!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fourteen! Thirteen!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Twelve! Eleven!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ten! Nine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eight! Seven!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:19:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Six! Five!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Four! Three!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Two! One!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva-01 has ceased operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Target is completely inactive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.67,0:20:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been three days now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Since they read us the riot act?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he stopped coming to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The transfer student, who else?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-I wonder what he's up to.\N-You worried about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said I was worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you're so bull-headed\Nin spite of being so socially awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.19,0:21:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had apologized\Nthe last time we saw him,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.20,0:21:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't have spent\Nthree whole days agonizing over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. This is the new kid's phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're worried, call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.02,0:22:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.42,0:23:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unable to get a handle on his feelings,{\i0}\N{\i1}Shinji runs away from even Misato.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, the organization{\i0}\N{\i1}unceremoniously drags him back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.85,0:23:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No one there had any kind words for him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.02,0:23:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next episode! "Rain, After Running Away"!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.85,0:23:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tune in next time{\i0}\N{\i1}for lots more fan service!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.40,0:23:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Translator: Dan Kanemitsu\NSubtitle Editor: David Fleming
